	* cfg.mk (local-checks-to-skip): Enable sc_makefile_check.
	* lib/Makefile.am (libgreputils_a_LIBADD): Use $(...), rather than
	anachronistic @...@ notation.
	* src/Makefile.am (LDADD): Likewise.
	* tests/Makefile.am (AWK): Remove definition.

