	* cfg.mk (local-checks-to-skip): Enable sc_trailing_blank.
	* AUTHORS: Remove trailing blanks.
	* COPYING: Likewise.
	* README: Likewise.
	* README-alpha: Likewise.
	* README-boot: Likewise.
